Class QuestionInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.ityx.mediatrix.data.PersonalRequeueInfo

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class QuestionInfo
extends PersonalRequeueInfo
implements Serializable
    The light object of the question. It contains only important informations. The class contains only required question informations to show a question in the browser tree.
